entries.content: The copyright organization SESAC engaged Duke Ellington to provide music during the annual convention of the National Association of Broadcasters. Here we present the actual dates, 6 and 7 April, and possibly the correct sequence of performances. They were not known when NDESOR IDs were assigned, so that they appear out of sequence between the two dates.
